## Structure universelle du prompt video

---

> Ordre recommande pour les generateurs IA (Gen-3, Kling, Seedance, Runway, etc.) :
>
> Mouvement de camera -> Sujet & action -> Cadre & ambiance -> Style visuel & lumiere -> Langage cinematographique

---

## 1. MOUVEMENT DE CAMERA

> Ce que fait la camera - rythme, direction et type de prise de vue.

### Types de mouvements

| Type | Description | Exemple |
|------|------------|---------|
| `Static camera` | Camera fixe | The camera is still, centered composition. |
| `Tracking shot` | Camera se deplace | Travelling backward shot through the corridor. |
| `Orbiting` | Camera tourne autour du sujet | Orbiting shot around the couple. |
| `Pan left/right` | Mouvement horizontal | Camera pans slowly to the right. |
| `Tilt up/down` | Mouvement vertical | Tilt down from ceiling to character's face. |
| `Handheld` | Tremble realiste | Dynamic handheld camera, documentary feeling. |
| `Steadicam` | Fluide et stable | Smooth Steadicam following shot. |
| `FPV` | Vue subjective | First-person view - immersive perspective. |

### Vitesse de mouvement

`Slow motion` | `Fast motion` | `Dynamic motion` | `Timelapse`

### Type de plan

`Wide shot`, `Medium shot`, `Close-up`, `Extreme close-up`,
`Over-the-shoulder`, `Two-person shot`, `Overhead`, `Symmetrical composition`

Astuce : combiner mouvement + plan + vitesse.

---

## 2. SUJET & ACTION

> Qui ou quoi est filme, et que fait-il ?

### Decrire le sujet

Formule :

(age + genre) + detail distinctif + posture ou expression

Exemples :

- A young woman with wet hair and porcelain skin.
- An elderly man in a beige coat holding a flickering lighter.
- Two dancers in a foggy room - bare feet, fragile gestures.

### Decrire l'action ou l'emotion

- She exhales slowly, lost in thought.
- He turns his head as light flickers across his face.
- The curtains move gently in the wind.
- Tears well up; he does not move.

Eviter gestes complexes et objets dynamiques.
Favoriser la subtilite emotionnelle.

---

## 3. CADRE & AMBIANCE

> Ou la scene se deroule et quelle sensation elle degage.

### Lieux possibles

`In an abandoned greenhouse`
`Inside a moving train`
`Under neon rain`
`By the sea at dusk`
`In a minimalist apartment`
`Foggy forest clearing`
`Deserted parking lot at night`
`Crowded subway station`

### Ambiances emotionnelles

`Melancholic`, `Romantic`, `Dreamlike`, `Tense`, `Poetic`,
`Mystical`, `Lonely`, `Surreal realism`, `Ethereal`, `Intimate`

### Details temporels

Heures : `Dawn`, `Morning`, `Afternoon light`, `Golden hour`, `Sunset`, `Night`

Meteo : `Rain`, `Fog`, `Snow`, `Overcast sky`, `Thunderstorm`, `Sunny haze`

Exemple :

In a foggy greenhouse, golden-hour sunlight filters through condensation, humid air shimmers with warmth.

---

## 4. STYLE VISUEL & LUMIERE

> Identite esthetique du plan : couleur, texture, contraste.

### Palette et contraste

`Desaturated colors`
`Muted tones`
`Low contrast`
`Soft diffusion`
`High contrast`
`Golden glow`
`Pastel tones`
`Bleached whites`
`Teal-and-orange look`

### Types d'eclairage

| Type | Effet |
|------|-------|
| `Diffused lighting` | Lumiere douce |
| `Backlit` | Silhouette dramatique |
| `Side lit` | Modelage sculptural |
| `Top lighting` | Mystere |
| `Golden-hour light` | Chaleur nostalgique |
| `Moonlight` | Reflet bleute |
| `Neon lighting` | Ton moderne |
| `Underwater glow` | Lumiere diffuse |

### Textures

`Fine film grain`
`Soft halation`
`Realistic DOF`
`Cinematic haze`
`Lens flare`
`Wet reflections`
`Subtle bloom`

---

## 5. LANGAGE CINEMATOGRAPHIQUE

> Parametres techniques et artistiques.

### Cameras modernes

ARRI Alexa Mini LF  
RED Komodo 6K  
Sony Venice 2  
Canon C700  

### Lenses

`35mm`
`85mm`
`24mm wide`
`Anamorphic lens`
`Macro lens`

### Film stocks

`Kodak Vision3 250D`
`Fuji Eterna 500T`
`CineStill 800T`
`Kodak Portra 400`

---

## Methode de construction

1. Mouvement de camera
2. Sujet & action
3. Cadre & ambiance
4. Style visuel
5. Langage cinematographique

---

## Conseils

Be specific.
Utilise un langage cinematographique clair.
Ne surcharge pas ton prompt.
